    description: {
      en: 'Found 2026-06-20 via ODS audit. Confirmed again against `Necrons ENG.ods` "Cryptek" sheet 2026-06-21: "May be upgraded to one of the following. Each specialisation is unique per army" (5 choices, +15pts each), "Dynasty Scion: The model gains an improved profile (see above) and has access to Lord equipment in the Armory, instead of Cryptek." FIXED (2026-06-21), design option (b) from this issue\'s own writeup — extended `Choice` with its own optional `variant_link` (engine/points.ts\'s `getActiveVariant` now checks per-choice links alongside the existing whole-group one, reusing the "one" constraint\'s built-in mutual exclusion instead of inventing a new cross-group exclusion field) and its own optional `unique_per_army` (validators.ts now checks per-CHOICE uniqueness keyed on (unitName, choice.name), not just whole-group/whole-variant uniqueness) — both fully generic, reusable by any future multi-choice group with the same shape. Also fixed, found during the same audit: the General Armory\'s "POINTS CRYPTEK"/"POINTS LORD" columns are mutually-exclusive TIERS (most items have only one or the other filled in — e.g. "War scythe"/"Lord of the Storm" have no Cryptek price at all), not a character/squad split; `isChar` being unconditionally true for Cryptek meant a base (non-Dynasty-Scion) Cryptek could illegally buy Lord-exclusive gear. New Necrons-Cryptek-specific branch in ArmoryModal.tsx prices off `activeVariant` instead. Buying Dynasty Scion now correctly swaps the Profile row, gates Armory tier, and blocks a 2nd Cryptek (of any squad) from picking the same specialisation.',
      de: 'Gefunden am 2026-06-20 per ODS-Audit. FIXED (2026-06-21): Choice erhält ein eigenes variant_link (getActiveVariant prüft jetzt auch pro Auswahl) und ein eigenes unique_per_army (Validator prüft jetzt pro-Auswahl-Eindeutigkeit). Zusätzlich behoben: die Cryptek/Lord-Preisspalten sind sich gegenseitig ausschließende Stufen, kein Charakter/Trupp-Splitting — ein Basis-Cryptek konnte fälschlich Lord-exklusive Ausrüstung kaufen, jetzt durch einen Necrons-Cryptek-spezifischen Zweig in ArmoryModal.tsx behoben.',
      es: 'Encontrado el 2026-06-20 vía auditoría ODS. ARREGLADO (2026-06-21): Choice ahora tiene su propio variant_link (getActiveVariant también revisa por opción) y su propio unique_per_army (el validador revisa unicidad por opción). También arreglado: las columnas de precio Cryptek/Lord son niveles mutuamente excluyentes, no una división personaje/escuadra — un Cryptek base podía comprar ilegalmente equipo exclusivo de Lord, ahora corregido con una rama específica de Necrons-Cryptek en ArmoryModal.tsx.',
    },
